::Incarcinator::

Incarcinator smiles at having hit Speedbreaker, but then is hit in the
side by a shot from Beastbox. He growls, flying upward further and
firing three shells at the shall bot.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> Speedbreaker had taken his attention away from Incinerator (dont
know
> why I did though :) and was not prepared. Two of the shells hit him
in
> the back, exploding with a loud blast of noise, and sent the
Decepticon
> falling towards Shockwave.
> 
> Beastbox on the other hand was glad that Incinerator had turned his
> attention to Speedbreaker. He maneuvered himself towards the enemy
now,
> closing the gap between them. He fired again as he aproached.
